text: Osvaldo Dorticós Torrado (17 April 1919 – 23 June 1983) was a Cuban politician. He was the president of Cuba from 1959 to 1976. He was a close ally of Cuban revolutionary and longtime leader Fidel Castro. ==References== Category:1919 births Category:1983 deaths Category:Presidents of Cuba
title: Osvaldo Dorticós Torrado
